@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<div class="container">
    <h1 class="mt-5 mb-3">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
</div>

<div class="container my-5">
    <p><em>Last updated: [Date]</em></p>

    <h2 class="mt-5">1. Who We Are</h2>
    <p>
        <strong>[Company Name]</strong><br>
        [Street Address]<br>
        [City, Country, ZIP Code]<br>
        Email: <a href="mailto:support@email.com">support@email.com</a><br>
        Phone: [+123456789]
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-5">2. What Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>User Information:</strong> Name, email, password (hashed), external login provider info.</li>
        <li><strong>Subtitle Files:</strong> Uploaded `.srt` files and translated output.</li>
        <li><strong>Credit & Payment Data:</strong> Credit usage, payment history. (We don't store full card data.)</li>
        <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> IP address, browser details, actions within the app.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-5">3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>To provide and maintain your user account.</li>
        <li>To process subtitle translation using OpenAI.</li>
        <li>To calculate token usage and deduct credits.</li>
        <li>To send you email notifications and updates.</li>
        <li>To improve app functionality and prevent fraud.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-5">4. Legal Basis for Processing</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Contractual necessity</strong> – Providing the service you signed up for.</li>
        <li><strong>Consent</strong> – When you choose to make translations public.</li>
        <li><strong>Legitimate interest</strong> – Analytics and fraud prevention.</li>
        <li><strong>Legal obligation</strong> – Compliance with applicable laws.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-5">5. Sharing Your Data</h2>
    <p>We only share data with trusted providers:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>OpenAI</strong> – For translation processing.</li>
        <li><strong>Stripe</strong> – For secure payments.</li>
        <li><strong>SendGrid</strong> – For email delivery.</li>
        <li><strong>Hosting provider</strong> – For secure file storage.</li>
        <li>Government authorities – When legally required.</li>
    </ul>
    <p><em>We never sell your personal data.</em></p>

    <h2 class="mt-5">6. Data Retention</h2>
    <p>
        We retain data:
        <ul>
            <li>While your account remains active.</li>
            <li>Translation files for [X months] (or until deleted).</li>
            <li>Payment records for [X years] (legal compliance).</li>
        </ul>
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-5">7. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You may request to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Access or correct your personal data.</li>
        <li>Delete your account or data.</li>
        <li>Download your data (data portability).</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent or object to processing.</li>
        <li>File a complaint with a data authority.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Contact us at <a href="mailto:support@email.com">support@email.com</a> to make any such request.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-5">8. Security Measures</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Encrypted HTTPS communication.</li>
        <li>Password hashing and secure storage.</li>
        <li>Access control and routine audits.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-5">9. International Transfers</h2>
    <p>
        If your data is stored or processed outside your country, we apply appropriate safeguards, such as Standard Contractual Clauses (SCCs).
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-5">10. Children’s Privacy</h2>
    <p>
        This app is not intended for users under 13. We do not knowingly collect data from minors.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-5">11. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>
        We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Major changes will be communicated via email or app notifications.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-5">12. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>
        Have questions? Contact us:<br>
        📧 <a href="mailto:support@email.com">support@email.com</a><br>
        📍 [Company Address]<br>
        🕒 [Business Hours]
    </p>
</div>

